STATE
v.
Michael M. WILLIAMS 242P17-1 Supreme Court of North Carolina. September 28, 2017 Michael A. Williams, for Williams, Michael M. Tracy Nayer, Assistant Attorney General, Kristy M. Newton, District Attorney, for State of North Carolina.

The following order has been entered on the motion filed on the 20th of July 2017 by Defendant for Petition for Discretionary Review:
